ingredientsDesc:
ARCHITECT SHBG Calibrators
6 Bottles (2.0 mL each) of ARCHITECT SHBG Calibrators. Calibrator A contains phosphate buffered saline with protein stabilizer. Calibrators B to F contain SHBG
ARCHITECT SHBG Controls
3×1 Bottle（4.0 mL each）of ARCHITECT SHBG Controls contain SHBG
ARCHITECT Reagent Kit, 100/400 Tests
Microparticles：1 or 4 Bottle（s）（6.6 mL each）Anti-SHBG coated microparticles in TRIS buffer. Preservative：sodium azide.
Conjugate：1 or 4 Bottle（s）（5.9 mL each）Anti-SHBG acridinium-labeled conjugate in phosphate buffer with protein（mouse, bovine）stabilizers. Preservative：sodium azide.
Assay Diluent：1 or 4 Bottle（s）（8.0 mL each）SHBG Assay Diluent containing phosphate buffer with protein （mouse, bovine）stabilizers. Preservative：sodium azide.
